    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to see this beauty go, but it's time for a new owner to experience the joy it brings. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this one\u2014honestly, it\u2019s about as close to showroom fresh as you can get. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, washed by hand every weekend, and drives just as smooth as the day I picked it up. You won't find a more pristine example out there. Swing by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I'm so proud of it!",
