      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical synergy. This S54-powered masterpiece has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance cycle, including a full VANOS bulletproofing and subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The 3.2L inline-six maintains perfect compression ratios, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual that delivers power through a refreshed limited-slip differential. Every bushing has been inspected, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum expansion tank to mitigate thermal fatigue. The paint depth is consistent across all factory panels, showcasing a finish that has been shielded from the elements. This is a turn-key, precision instrument for the driver who demands peak atmospheric performance and a documented pedigree.",
      "price": 44850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
